{"tid":2436321,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"暗戀一個人其實好攰阿","createTime":"2021-03-07T05:02:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-07T08:45:46.000Z","uid":394103,"like":12,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"463cb3515c27679b3bef2b3c3d05667d7066c279","tid":2436321,"uid":394103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T05:02:21.000Z","msg":"想開po好耐<br />\n個人開始大啦 廿幾歲仲係A0<br />\n暗戀左一個人差唔多4-5年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都因為佢拒絕左其他人既表白，因為清楚自己絕對唔會係騎牛搵馬既人<br />\n更加唔會因為想出pool，求其同人一齊左先<br />\n個個人係我老豆多年兄弟個仔，識左好多年<br />\n細個個陣會多啲一齊玩<br />\n大個可能大家都忙 <br />\n所以都係新年一年見得個一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第一個印象覺得佢好有禮貌同斯文，講野又有文有路<br />\n好少見啲男仔會主動幫手斟茶招呼客人<br />\n對住佢有種小鹿亂撞既感覺<br />\n會變得唔敢同佢講野 不過因為啲大人都係到<br />\n費時尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多數對佢知既野都由我老豆轉達比我知<br />\n不過我老豆唔知我暗戀既人就係佢<br />\n有時都會有好多幻想<br />\n佢咁優秀，可能佢都已經有女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以前成日叫啲人鍾意就表白啦，當燒到埋黎自己就淆撚哂底，好驚衰左搞到日後尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n原來暗戀人係咁辛苦，一個人個陣會諗咁多野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無巴絲打都會有呢種感覺？"},{"pid":"d0436e7304872c13c2dd7942cef3ba983cb2d1d3","tid":2436321,"uid":58201,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T05:05:26.000Z","msg":"咁耐冇見 平時都已經冇咩交集<br />\n仲諗表白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce4b99f7d70e8edffaf3eedf3d7acac5127c3038","tid":2436321,"uid":283908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T05:06:16.000Z","msg":"冇啊"},{"pid":"ad40a4e3ddb256a2d0e264fbb37675c473bcbf45","tid":2436321,"uid":131232,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T05:10:28.000Z","msg":"dont ff too much<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a9b33b537a32de2f2cfd3262a90e21194cd7bc5","tid":2436321,"uid":394103,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d0436e7304872c13c2dd7942cef3ba983cb2d1d3","tid":2436321,"uid":58201,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T05:05:26.000Z","msg":"咁耐冇見 平時都已經冇咩交集<br />\n仲諗表白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T05:11:34.000Z","msg":"都係既 <br />\n每次都就黎忘記呢啲事<br />\n一到新年又見，又諗起又會勾起條引<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個腦好似不能控制咁<br />\n如果知道佢已經有女朋友，咁個陣真係會正式放低了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce99b69ae7527a1a94d834f031a6016ddc6d765e","tid":2436321,"uid":3302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T05:11:52.000Z","msg":"唔好著底褲上佢屋企俾佢屌"},{"pid":"07bcc2c7d48b704d628e88fcc91c58f21bc9a428","tid":2436321,"uid":394103,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ad40a4e3ddb256a2d0e264fbb37675c473bcbf45","tid":2436321,"uid":131232,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T05:10:28.000Z","msg":"dont ff too much<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T05:12:11.000Z","msg":"Ff永遠都係最美好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6d77489eeb60bdd388444ae26574ff0db2c4e58","tid":2436321,"uid":58201,"like":